title: Pineapple Grapefruit By Juice Head
description: Juice Head Pineapple Grapefruit is a delicious pairing of sweet golden pineapple with a zesty burst of pink grapefruit for an exciting tropical vape sensation. This enticing exotic fruit e-liquid delivers a mouthwatering summer fruit vapor that'll dazzle your taste buds with a refreshing blend of sweet and tangy fruit goodness that will rock your world.
